task: Turn wifi off through the settings app.

action.description: Swipe up from the bottom of the screen to open the app drawer.
Launch the Settings app to access Wi-Fi settings.
Tap on the "Network & internet" option to access Wi-Fi settings.
Tap on the "Internet" option to access Wi-Fi settings.
Tap the Wi-Fi toggle switch to turn off Wi-Fi.
